521 int get_current_time()
522 {
523  time_t timestamp;
524  struct tm * t;
525  timestamp = time(NULL);
526  t = localtime(&timestamp);
527 
528 
529  sprintf(tmp_time,"%02uh %02umin %02usec", t->tm_hour, t->tm_min, t->tm_sec);
530 
531  return(0);
532 }

537 int load_midipreset()
538 {
539 char temp_folder_midi[256];
540 sprintf(temp_folder_midi,"%s\\midi_presets\\%s",mondirectory,midipreset_name);
541 chdir(temp_folder_midi);
542 FILE *fpm;
543 
544 if ((fpm=fopen(file_midi_affectation, "rb"))==NULL)
545 { sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Error opening file %s", file_midi_affectation);b_report_error[idf]=1;}
546 else
547 {
548 sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Opening file %s", file_midi_affectation);
549 if (fread(miditable, sizeof(int),midi_affectation_size, fpm) !=midi_affectation_size)
550 { sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Error Loaded %s", file_midi_affectation);b_report_error[idf]=1;}
551 else sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Loaded file %s", file_midi_affectation);
552 }
553 
554 if ((fpm=fopen(file_midi_send_out, "rb"))==NULL)
555 { sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Error opening file %s", file_midi_send_out);b_report_error[idf]=1;}
556 else
557 {
558 sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Opening file %s", file_midi_send_out);
559 if (fread(midi_send_out, sizeof(bool),midi_send_out_size, fpm) !=midi_send_out_size)
560 { sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Error Loaded %s", file_midi_send_out);b_report_error[idf]=1;}
561 else sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"Loaded file %s", file_midi_send_out);
562 }
563 load_Fader_state_to_midi_array();
564 fclose(fpm);
565 //REROLL
566 sprintf(rep,"");
567 sprintf(rep,"%s",mondirectory);
568 chdir (rep);
569 
570  return(0);
571 }

574 int Show_report_save_load()
575 {
576 Rect Report_Save_Load(Vec2D(report_SL_X, report_SL_Y), Vec2D( 350,160));
577 Report_Save_Load.SetRoundness(15);
578 Report_Save_Load.SetLineWidth(epaisseur_ligne_fader*3);
579 Report_Save_Load.Draw(CouleurFond);
580 Report_Save_Load.DrawOutline(CouleurLigne);
581 if(window_focus_id==W_SAVEREPORT){Report_Save_Load.DrawOutline(CouleurFader);}
582 
583 //+ minus debug
584 //Plus Minus buttons debug show
585 Rect MinusPosMyRep(Vec2D(report_SL_X+290,report_SL_Y+76),Vec2D(50,20));
586 MinusPosMyRep.SetRoundness(7.5);
587 MinusPosMyRep.SetLineWidth(epaisseur_ligne_fader);
588 Rect PlusPosMyRep(Vec2D(report_SL_X+290,report_SL_Y+106),Vec2D(50,20));
589 PlusPosMyRep.SetRoundness(7.5);
590 PlusPosMyRep.SetLineWidth(epaisseur_ligne_fader);
591 
592 for(int co=0;co<10;co++)
593 {
594 Rect AlarmFile(Vec2D((report_SL_X+5),(report_SL_Y+52+(10*co))),Vec2D(300,12));
595 AlarmFile.SetRoundness(5);
596 if(b_report_error[co+position_view_line]==1)
597 {
598  AlarmFile.Draw(Rgba::RED.WithAlpha(alpha_blinker));
599 }
600 petitchiffre.Print( ol::ToString(co+position_view_line),(report_SL_X+5), (report_SL_Y+60+(10*co)));
601 petitchiffre.Print( string_save_load_report[co+position_view_line],(report_SL_X+30), (report_SL_Y+60+(10*co)));
602 }
603 
604 MinusPosMyRep.Draw(CouleurFond);
605 PlusPosMyRep.Draw(CouleurFond);
606 if(window_focus_id==W_SAVEREPORT)
607 {
608 if(mouse_x>report_SL_X+290 && mouse_x<report_SL_X+340)
609 {
610 
611 //-
612  if( mouse_y>report_SL_Y+76 && mouse_y<report_SL_Y+96)
613  {
614  MinusPosMyRep.Draw(CouleurSurvol);
615  if(mouse_button==1 && mouse_released==0 )
616  {
617  MinusPosMyRep.Draw(CouleurFader);
618  position_view_line-=5;
619  if(position_view_line<0) {position_view_line=0; }
620  }
621  }
622 //+
623  if( mouse_y>report_SL_Y+106 && mouse_y<report_SL_Y+136)
624  {
625  PlusPosMyRep.Draw(CouleurSurvol);
626  if(mouse_button==1 && mouse_released==0 )
627  {
628  PlusPosMyRep.Draw(CouleurFader);
629  position_view_line+=5;
630  if(position_view_line>(255-10)) {position_view_line=(255-10); }
631  }
632  }
633 
634 }
635 
636 }
637 
638 MinusPosMyRep.DrawOutline(CouleurLigne);
639 PlusPosMyRep.DrawOutline(CouleurLigne);
640 petitchiffre.Print("line -",report_SL_X+300, report_SL_Y+90);
641 petitchiffre.Print("line +",report_SL_X+300, report_SL_Y+120);
642 
643 
644 
645 
646 petitchiffre.Print( mondirectory,(report_SL_X+10+90), (report_SL_Y+20));
647 petitchiffre.Print( nomduspectacle,(report_SL_X+10+90), (report_SL_Y+35));
648 
649 
650 return(0);
651 }

656 int load_onstart_config()
657 {
658  FILE *cfg_file = NULL ;
659  char read_buff_winfil[ 512 ] ;
660  int it=0;
661  cfg_file = fopen("user/config_onstart.txt", "rt" );
662  if( !cfg_file )
663  {
664  sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"!config_onstart.txt");
665  }
666  else
667  {
668  //premiere ligne les args
669  if( !fgets( read_buff_winfil , sizeof( read_buff_winfil ) ,cfg_file ) )
670  {
671  sprintf(string_save_load_report[idf],"! config_onstart.txt");
672  }
673 
674  fscanf( cfg_file , "%d / %d / %d / %d /\n" , &load_camera_on_start, &open_arduino_on_open , &enable_iCat, &expert_mode);
675 
676  fclose( cfg_file );
677  }
678 return(0);
679 }
